name: RiggingJs
shortDescription: Open-source react.js application, that takes the keypoints generated by the face mesh tensorflow.js model, then map the movement that the person is doing in front of the camera into a 3d model
longDescription: Open-source react.js application, that takes the keypoints generated by the face mesh tensorflow.js model, then map the movement that the person is doing in front of the camera into a 3d model
